    "Details": "A knock sounds on your office door and you call out, \"Come in...\"\r\n\r\nThe door opens and Darius strides in with a somber look on his face, \"Commander, we were just unloading the cargo from one of our supply runs, and I noticed the coffin containing the body of [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] was on the manifest.\"\r\n\r\nYou slump back in your chair, \"What?!?  No way... what happened?\"\r\n\r\nDarius sighs, \"According to the attached holovid recording, [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] attempted a radical maneuver to try and take out their assigned drone target.  Unfortunately, it ended up with their LAM slamming into a radio tower.  They died instantly.  How do you want to proceed?\"",
